label: uncl4343
comment: Code specifying the type of acknowledgment required or transmitted.

values.label: Debit advice
values.comment: Receiver of the payment message needs to return a debit advice in response to the payment message.

values.label: Message acknowledgement
values.comment: Indicates that an acknowledgement relating to receipt of message is required.

values.label: Acknowledge - with detail and change
values.comment: Acknowledge complete including changes.

values.label: Acknowledge - with detail, no change
values.comment: Acknowledge complete without changes.

values.label: Debit advice for each transaction
values.comment: A debit advice is requested for each transaction in the message.

values.label: Debit advice/message acknowledgement
values.comment: The sender wishes to receive both a Debit Advice and an acknowledgement of receipt for a payment message.

values.label: Authentication
values.comment: Authentication, by a party, of a document established for him by another party.

values.label: Debit advice/message acknowledgement for each transaction
values.comment: A debit advice and message acknowledgement are requested for each transaction in the message.

values.label: Acknowledge only changes
values.comment: Acknowledgement of changes only is required.

values.label: Pending
values.comment: Indication that the referenced offer or transaction (e.g. cargo booking or quotation request) is being dealt with.

values.label: Return only TIR transport information
values.comment: The sender of the message expects only TIR (Transports Internationaux Routiers) transport information in return.

values.label: Return only declaration information
values.comment: Desc The sender of the message expects only declaration information in return.

values.label: Return only guarantee information
values.comment: The sender of the message expects only guarantee information in return.

values.label: Return all information regarding guarantee
values.comment: The sender of the message expects all information regarding the guarantee in return.

values.label: Accepted
values.comment: Indication that the referenced offer or transaction (e.g., cargo booking or quotation request) has been accepted.

values.label: Response expected
values.comment: The sender of the message expects a response.

values.label: Direct documentary credit collection
values.comment: Documentary credit collection forwarded directly.

values.label: Credit advice and message acknowledgement
values.comment: The receiver of the message is to acknowledge receipt of the message and sent a credit advice for each credit.

values.label: Conditionally accepted
values.comment: Indication that the referenced offer or transaction (e.g., cargo booking or quotation request) has been accepted under conditions indicated in this message.

values.label: Confirmation of measurements
values.comment: Indication that the message contains the physical measurements on which the charges will be based.

values.label: No acknowledgement needed
values.comment: Specifies that no acknowledgement is needed in response to this message.

values.label: Rejected
values.comment: Indication that the referenced offer or transaction (e.g., cargo booking or quotation request) is not accepted.

values.label: Credit advice
values.comment: The message recipient is to send a credit advice in response to the message.

values.label: Acknowledgement when error
values.comment: An acknowledgement is requested when an error occurred.

values.label: Acknowledgment due to error
values.comment: An acknowledgment is sent because an error was identified in the received message.

values.label: Alternate date
values.comment: The solution proposed in the response applies to another date than the one requested.

values.label: Alternate service
values.comment: The solution proposed in the response applies to another service than the one requested.
